*.token
*.key
.env
.env.*

# Personal personas the user wrote (only the curated examples ship)
personas/*.md
!personas/friendly-tutor.md
!personas/concise-coder.md
.hydra-index/

# Local-only docs that intentionally don't ship.
RELEASE.md
